new.name: CVE-2021-3129---Laravel-RCE
new.description:
## About The script has been made for exploiting the Laravel RCE (CVE-2021-3129) vulnerability.
This script allows you to write/execute commands on a website running Laravel <= v8.4.2, that has "APP_DEBUG" set to "true" in its ".env" file.
